What you need to know:

In the South Rift, there’s a big fight between Nakuru Senator Susan Kihika and Bahati MP Kimani Ngunjiri, with 2022 county governorship politics at play.In Mt Kenya, Mathira MP Rigathi Gachagua, Kikuyu’s Kimani Ichung’wa and Meru Senator Mithika Linturi have moved to cut Mr Kuria’s legs, saying UDA was the only ‘hustler party’ in the region.